r_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The following compiles on 64-bit usize platforms, albeit with a warning:\r\n\r\nIt compiles because it ends up with `[u8; 0]` implementing `Foo`.\r\n\r\n```rust\r\ntrait Foo { }\r\n\r\nimpl Foo for [u8; 0x1_0000_0000_0000_0000] { }\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let _b = Box::new([]) as Box<Foo>;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe warning is right:\r\n\r\n```\r\nwarning: literal out of range for usize\r\n```\r\n\r\nRustc should consider making this a hard error.\r\n\r\nRust version: rustc 1.23.0-nightly (e340996ff 2017-11-02)", "closed_by": {"login": "oli-obk", "id": 332036, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzMjAzNg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/332036?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk", "html_url": "https://github.com/oli-obk", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/45745/reactions", "total_count": 3, "+1": 2, "-1": 0, "laugh": 1, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/45745/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}